org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.tigr.contig

Interface TigrContigVisitor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractTigrContigBuilderVisitor

    public interface TigrContigVisitor
    TigrContigVisitor is a visitor interface to visit a single contigs inside a TIGR .contig encoded file. The id of the contig has already been given by TigrContigFileVisitor.visitContig(TigrContigFileVisitor.TigrContigVisitorCallback, String).
    Author:
    dkatzel

    • Method Detail

      • visitConsensus

        void visitConsensus(NucleotideSequence consensus)
        Visit the consensus of this contig.
        Parameters:
        consensus - the consensus sequence of this contig; will not be null.

      • visitRead

        TigrContigReadVisitor visitRead(String readId,
                                long gappedStartOffset,
                                Direction dir,
                                Range validRange)
        A new read has been detected.
        Parameters:
        readId - the read id.
        gappedStartOffset - the start offset of this read into the gapped consensus in 0-based coordinates.
        dir - the Direction of this read.
        validRange - the Range of the "good" portion of this entire full length, untrimmed read sequence that provides coverage to this contig.
        Returns:
        a TigrContigReadVisitor instance if this read should be visited; if null is returned, then this read will not be visited.
